{"tid":1355623,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【緊急文宣】紅底報導祖墳隻字不提黑社會","createTime":"2019-07-23T10:42:32.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-23T11:52:49.000Z","uid":107092,"like":30,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"147224fcfce3f0277e595cd7a349bab87f0bd8a3","tid":1355623,"uid":107092,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-23T10:42:32.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/irUu5mZ.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FirUu5mZ.png&h=1cbd164c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/NE7o9OD.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FNE7o9OD.png&h=99242849&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\n<br />\n唔貼link避免增加觀看次數，<br />\n大致上就係唔揀白衫佬留名嘅圖片嚟報導，<br />\n將事源全部怪罪網民。<br />\n預計今晚CCTVB報導都會用同樣方法，<br />\n文宣圖片應該要揀返有白衫黑社會留名嘅圖片嚟宣揚返事實，<br />\n本人在此強烈譴責白衫鄉黑破壞祖墳洩憤！<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"49c500be35342ef05190fe74415f69f3920c8c71","tid":1355623,"uid":27946,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-07-23T10:44:56.000Z","msg":"唔係話佢無找數比白衫佬搞返轉頭咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9b0f93bc0e59ddd7bdd32dc3ec46caa70b52b65a","tid":1355623,"uid":107092,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"49c500be35342ef05190fe74415f69f3920c8c71","tid":1355623,"uid":27946,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-07-23T10:44:56.000Z","msg":"唔係話佢無找數比白衫佬搞返轉頭咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-23T10:46:19.000Z","msg":"明顯將矛頭指返落普通市民身上，預計CCTVB都會用同樣手法。"},{"pid":"25ca1fb4dac7dc45f8704839bd6966264dae7de6","tid":1355623,"uid":224095,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-23T10:46:40.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/aRU65OY.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FaRU65OY.png&h=f1b891a7&s={SIZE}\" />"},{